channel.title: Need help to get rid of kills and deaths on screen
channel.description: I don't know why it was here I removed the option to browse someones goods when you right click them now this comes up. http://tinypic.com/r/in8vpv/6 Also now at duel arena there is no challenge and in wild there is no attack option how do i add thoughs now?

item.title: Need help to get rid of kills and deaths on screen
item.dc:creator: @Tutorial Tutorial
item.description:
@Tutorial wrote:

[quote=“darkageisme, post:5, topic:478007”][quote author=Tutorial link=topic=596205.msg4197727#msg4197727 date=1357764956]

The kills and deaths are probably being loaded from your client’s interface class.

No its on the client and its also on my webclient.

Have you checked? By the way, the webclient is nothing more than a Java applet in the form of a JAR.
[/quote]
yeah but i did not compile the client just made a weblient does not have everything the real client does.[/quote]
That makes no sense at all.

Read full topic
